    // An person i > pos is visible if and only if they choose 'R'.
    // We need exactly 'k_R' people from the right to choose 'R', where 0 <= k_R <= rightCount.
    // The number of ways to choose exactly k_R people from 'rightCount' is C(rightCount, k_R).

